---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Robotic Case Packing — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="Fully managed robotic case packing systems for food, beverage, and CPG manufacturers — month-to-month pricing, 24/7 support, and results from day one. No capital required."
  ogTitle="Robotic Case Packing — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed robotic case packing. Month-to-month pricing, 24/7 support, no capital required."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/packing" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .cp-bgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px}
    .cp-bcell{background:var(--white);padding:28px 26px}
    .cp-bcell h3{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 8px}
    .cp-bcell p{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.6;color:var(--mgrey);margin:0}
    .cp-faq{border-top:1px solid var(--lgrey);padding:22px 0}
    .cp-faq:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .cp-faq dt{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 8px}
    .cp-faq dd{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.65;color:var(--mgrey);margin:0}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>Case Packing
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Case Packing</div>
    <h1>Robotic Case Packing.<br><em>No Capital Required.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Fully managed case packing systems for food, beverage, and CPG manufacturers: month-to-month pricing, 24/7 support, and results from day one.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/CasepackerPromoVideo_NoText_poster.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · case packing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why Automate</div>
      <h2>Cut costs and improve line accuracy, <em>automatically</em>.</h2>
      <p>Case packing has always leaned on manual labor, but hiring, training, and retaining packers only gets harder. Demand spikes, multiplying SKUs, and labor shortages expose the real cost: inconsistent output, rising costs, and bottlenecks. Formic's fully managed robotic case packing eliminates those challenges from day one.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Vision-guided placement — correct orientation, secure pack, fewer defects</li>
        <li>Predictable cycle times that feed throughput up and down the line</li>
        <li>Reallocate packers to higher-value, higher-retention roles</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://land.formic.co/case-packing-quick-start-checklist" class="larr">Case packing quick-start checklist →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/solutions/case-packer.jpg" alt="Formic robotic case packer on a production line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Robotic case packing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag">Results from day one</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 4px">Why manufacturers <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">automate case packing</em>.</h2>
    <div class="cp-bgrid">
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Uninterrupted, high-speed production</h3><p>Robots run around the clock at peak performance — no fatigue, breaks, shift changes, or absenteeism slowing the line.</p></div>
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Accurate, consistent packing</h3><p>Vision-guided movements place every product correctly and securely — fewer defects, less rework, a higher-quality finished product.</p></div>
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Reduced rework and product damage</h3><p>Handling is tailored to your product's fragility, shape, and packaging format, protecting margins and customer trust.</p></div>
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Adaptable to high-mix SKUs</h3><p>Flexible, programmable systems handle frequent changeovers and SKU variation, so agility never costs you throughput.</p></div>
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Lower labor costs, higher productivity</h3><p>Reallocate hard-to-retain packers to higher-value roles — reliable, repeatable output with less turnover and training overhead.</p></div>
      <div class="cp-bcell"><h3>Improved safety and ergonomics</h3><p>Automation removes the repetitive strain of manual packing, reducing injury claims and improving morale.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/CasepackerPromoVideo_NoText.gif" alt="Formic Top Load Case Packer packing cases" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Top Load Case Packer</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Formic Case Packer</div>
      <h2>The Top Load <em>Case Packer</em>.</h2>
      <p>Pre-designed for rigid primary packaging into cases or trays. Fits tight floors, handles higher line speeds and weights.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Packs jars, cartons, canisters, cans, cups, bottles, tubs, bowls, clamshells & more</li>
        <li>Unit weights up to 20 lbs</li>
        <li>Pack rates up to 100 units/min</li>
        <li>Compact 8' × 8' × 7' footprint</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get the Top Load data sheet →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Specialized Systems</div>
      <h2>Specialized Systems <em>built for your line</em>.</h2>
      <p>Bottles, bags, pouches, or oddly shaped products. The Formic solutions engineering team scopes and designs the right system for your line — delta robots, traditional drop packing, or vision-guided pick-and-place — built for your SKUs and packaging requirements.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Pick products directly from upstream conveyors or accumulation points</li>
        <li>Detect orientation and make real-time adjustments</li>
        <li>Place products into cases in the exact configuration needed</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Scope my line →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Talos-0095.jpg">
        <source src="/ATLAS_EOAT.webm" type="video/webm" />
      </video>
      <span class="img-cap">Delta to drop packing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:flex-start">What's Included</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4.4vw,64px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.04;color:var(--white);margin:10px 0 14px">One flat monthly fee. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Zero capital required.</em></h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,245,241,.62);max-width:720px;margin:0 0 6px">You don't spend CapEx on the equipment. You don't worry about repairs. You don't pay for downtime. You just get results from day one.</p>
    <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(240,245,241,.62);max-width:720px;margin:0 0 18px">And the fastest deployment on the market.</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>System design and layout</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>All robots, grippers, and parts</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Software, programming, and controls</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>On-site installation and training</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Ongoing service and corrective maintenance</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>24/7 monitoring and support</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px">
    <div class="db-tag">FAQ</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(30px,3.6vw,48px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.06;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 22px">Case packing <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">questions</em>.</h2>
    <dl style="margin:0">
      <div class="cp-faq"><dt>Will it integrate with our existing equipment?</dt><dd>Absolutely. Our case packers are designed to work with your existing setup.</dd></div>
      <div class="cp-faq"><dt>What if something goes wrong?</dt><dd>Formic provides 24/7 bilingual support and corrective maintenance. This is all included in your monthly fee, with performance SLAs written into every agreement.</dd></div>
      <div class="cp-faq"><dt>Is training required?</dt><dd>Training is provided, and the systems are simple for your team to operate.</dd></div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Lock in your counts.<br><em>Lock in your line.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
